<DIV><FONT color=#cccccc></FONT>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV><FONT color=#cccccc><STRONG>/useitem slot_number</STRONG></FONT></DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>That function would essentially "activate" whatever item is in the specific slot number.&nbsp; The function /stopsong does work to stop clicked songs (log in and test), and they have a /stopcast button for non-song clickies.&nbsp; All they need is the /useitem slot_num function and it'll be complete.&nbsp;&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
